    <title>Authentication Endpoints</title>
    <para>You can use the Rackspace Cloud Identity authentication endpoints from version 1.1 or
        version 2.0. The legacy v1.1 API endpoint only supports authentication services, but you can
        use tokens from version 1.1 in version 2.0 API calls.</para>
    <important><para>If your Rackspace Cloud account requires multi-factor authentication, you can authenticate
            only with Identity API version 2.0 or later.</para></important>
